<p>Using <a href="http://nodejs.org/download/" target="_blank">a package</a>:</p>
<p><em>Simply <a href="http://nodejs.org/download/" target="_blank">download Windows Installer</a>.</em></p>
<p>Using <a href="http://chocolatey.org" target="_blank">chocolatey</a> to install <a href="http://chocolatey.org/packages/nodejs" target="_blank">Node</a>:</p>
<pre><code>cinst nodejs
</code></pre><p>or for <a href="http://chocolatey.org/packages/nodejs.install" target="_blank">full install with NPM</a>:</p>
<pre><code>cinst nodejs.install
</code></pre><h2 id="on-to-sails-js-" permalink="on-to-sailsjs">On to Sails.js!</h2>
